name: Crown Box
description: The Crown Box adds a royal touch to any space. Currently made to order 5-6 weeks. Handmade. Shagreen/Pen Shell, wood veneer interior. Wipe clean with soft dry cloth. Made in Philippines. All shagreen-covered items should be kept out of direct sunlight, color variants may occur on the stingray and other exotic finishes, but this showcases the Parisian label's commitment to creating authentic luxurious products using natural components.
